         ( 3 x   +   y   ^   2 )   *   abs ( sin ( x )   +   cos ( y )) 
     end  X   =   repmat ( x ' , length ( y ), 1 )  Y   =   repmat ( y , 1 , length ( x ))  Z   =   map ( f , X , Y )  p1   =   contour ( x , y , f , fill = true )  p2   =   contour ( x , y , Z )  plot ( p1 , p2 )

